data22.household = haven::read_dta("R://mhs2022d-g/MHS2022HHD.dta")
data22.person = haven::read_dta("R://mhs2022d-g/MHS2022SPL.dta")
data22 <- left_join(data22.household, data22.person) 
original.labels = var_label(data22)

data = readRDS("data_suicide.rds")%>%
  filter(Age <=76)

imp_data = readRDS("imputed_data_suicide.rds")  
imp_data = lapply(imp_data,function(x){x %>% filter(Age <= 76)})

Survival analysis

Censor at age 25

surv.var = c("AFSUICAT","AFSTPLAN","AFSTTHGT","SHAGE1")

exposure = "Agegroup"

confounders = c("GenDiverse","Sexorient","ATSI","CALD")

for(var in surv.var){
  
# create survival data
surv.data = data %>%
  mutate(time = as.numeric(ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0, Age,!!sym(var))),
         status = ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0,0,1),
         status = ifelse(time > 25,0,status),
         time = ifelse(time > 25, 25, time)
         )
  
surv.data_imp =  lapply(imp_data, function(x){ x %>%
  mutate(time = as.numeric(ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0, Age,!!sym(var))),
         status = ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0,0,1),
         status = ifelse(time > 25,0,status),
         time = ifelse(time > 25, 25, time)
         )})

print(original.labels[[var]])
# fit coxph model
SurvivalTable(exposure,confounders,surv.data,imp_dta = surv.data_imp, MI = TRUE)

}

stratified by birth cohort, censor at 25

surv.var = c("AFSUICAT","AFSTPLAN","AFSTTHGT","SHAGE1")
confounders = c("GenDiverse","Sexorient","ATSI","CALD",
               "CLOSEATT","LTHYNKR",
               "ICD_MHH","ICD_ANXH","ICD_AFFH","ICD_SUB",
               "PT13","PT22_1","sexually_assaulted_before19")
exposure = NULL

for(i in confounders)attr(data[[i]],'label') <- original.labels[[i]]

store.results = NULL
for(var in surv.var){
  for(agegroup in levels(data$Agegroup)){
  
# create survival data
surv.data = data %>%
  filter(Agegroup == agegroup) %>%
  mutate(time = as.numeric(ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0, AGEP,!!sym(var))),
         status = ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0,0,1),
         status = ifelse(time > 25,0,status),
         time = ifelse(time > 25, 25, time)) 

surv.data_imp =  lapply(imp_data, function(x){ x %>%
  filter(Agegroup == agegroup) %>%
  mutate(time = as.numeric(ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0, Age,!!sym(var))),
         status = ifelse(!!sym(var)>=97|!!sym(var)==0,0,1),
         status = ifelse(time > 25,0,status),
         time = ifelse(time > 25, 25, time)
         )})

print(original.labels[[var]])
print(agegroup)

# fit coxph model
store.results = rbind(store.results,
                      SurvivalTable(exposure,confounders,surv.data,imp_dta = surv.data_imp, MI = TRUE) %>%
  mutate(var = var,
         agegroup = agegroup))

}
}
